<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Us - Kakwara Hospital</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #005b96;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .header {
      background: #005b96;
      color: white;
      padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #2563eb;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .mission-vision {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 2rem;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 300px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .card img {
      max-width: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
      position: relative;
    }

    .timeline li {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
      background: white;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
    }

    .timeline li span {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2563eb;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .feature {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 280px;
      background: white;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #2563eb;
    }

    .feature:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      background: #005b96;
      color: #f8fafc;
    }

    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { transform: translateY(-30px); opacity: 0; }
      to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { transform: translateY(30px); opacity: 0; }
      to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <h1>Kakwara Hospital</h1>
    <p>Excellence in Care. Compassion in Service.</p>
    <a href={~p"/main"} 
   style="
   margin-left: auto;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      background: transparent;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.3rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
   ">
   <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i> Home
</a>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">Kakwara Hospital is a state-of-the-art medical institution providing a wide range of healthcare services. We prioritize patient well-being with top-quality medical staff, modern facilities, and compassionate service.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section mission-vision">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/100/4a90e2/hospital-room.png" alt="Mission icon">
      <h3>Our Mission</h3>
      <p>Deliver high-quality, patient-centered healthcare with excellence, empathy, and innovation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/100/4a90e2/stethoscope.png" alt="Vision icon">
      <h3>Our Vision</h3>
      <p>To be a regional and global leader in healthcare innovation and compassionate service.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Our Journey</h2>
    <ul class="timeline">
      <li><span>2005</span> - Kakwara Hospital was founded with a vision for accessible community healthcare.</li>
      <li><span>2010</span> - Introduced specialty care units including Pediatrics, Surgery, and Obstetrics.</li>
      <li><span>2015</span> - ISO certified, and expanded to a 200-bed facility with digital patient records.</li>
      <li><span>2022</span> - Launched a comprehensive telemedicine platform and modern diagnostics center.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Why Choose Kakwara</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature">
        <i class="fas fa-hospital"></i>
        <h4>Advanced Infrastructure</h4>
        <p>Modern buildings and specialized departments for all patient needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <i class="fas fa-ambulance"></i>
        <h4>24/7 Emergency</h4>
        <p>Round-the-clock ambulance and emergency care units ready to respond.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
        <h4>Expert Staff</h4>
        <p>Skilled physicians, nurses, and support teams delivering exceptional care.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 Kakwara Hospital. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
